Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.62,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.70,0:00:51.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.97,0:00:58.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.98,0:01:03.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:12.89,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.50,0:01:27.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.94,0:01:35.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.22,0:01:42.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.32,0:01:53.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.59,0:02:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}精打细算的亚力克斯\NCalculate Alex
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，把板手拿给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,板手找到了，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我记得你不是枪兵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械你会修吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别看我这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家我也是有知识有技术的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比普通的机械师要可靠多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个好消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既然是机械师就早说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N这下总算可以有个后辈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着啊\N其实我只是个枪兵而已呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对机械是一窍不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先这套制服得想点办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械师就要有机械师的样子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上次不是救了你们吗\N这次换你们来救我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要麻烦人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲等合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝，从现在起你就是\N银之战舰维修班的一员了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他表现得不够高兴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴就给我笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你找到新的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，副舰长有事找你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说苏菲亚小姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八小时耐力赛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说银之战舰现在\N正在驶往地平洞窟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道地平洞窟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是先锋艇驾驶员\N没有人会不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的八小时耐力赛\N是每个人都想挑战的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比赛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N一个有点与众不同的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比赛必须使用\N现场所准备的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.11,0:04:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了想办法\N让破烂不堪的先锋艇飞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在当场进行调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午夜零点的时候\N飞在最前面的机体就算冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点是必须持续飞八个小时哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是驾驶员而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也考验了机械师的本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有团队合作的趣味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要不要参加比赛看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以参加吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，只要你们有那个意愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们只有两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么组队呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会派葛温他们跟着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就能参加了耶，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，我们参加吧，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿你也是跟我们一队的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞒你说\N当我决心留在这里时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已经放弃参加比赛的念头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我实在很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，苏菲亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去做出赛的准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会觉得\N没办法再参加比赛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里\N驾驶先锋艇就是为了战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是银之战舰而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.72,0:05:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回这片天空真正的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.19,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟早有一天必须借重你们这些\N先锋艇驾驶员的力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这天一定会来到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，请小心慢走\N银之战舰就交给我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只需要想着比赛的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才塔台那里传来报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀无赦的\N银之战舰一行人抵达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀无赦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来今夜会是个\N难得的开心之夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诺兹侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下角色都到齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戏可以开幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走向毁灭的最后一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的沙漏呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，还不快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第225届地平洞窟\N八小时耐力赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇抽选即将开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请各位驾驶员集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要抽到一架好机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶技术比较重要啦\N我们也去吧，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.22,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色六号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自奥格兰的戴姆与卡多加队\N抽到的是蓝色六号的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是黑色十号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是来自诺齐亚的\N克劳士与拉薇队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿你去抽签
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去抽出最好的签吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是位可爱的先锋艇驾驶员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西飞得起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比传闻中的还要惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么破成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说每年只有个位数的机体\N能够飞完全程呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忍不住手痒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们，干活啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下可有得忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得在三个小时里\N让这家伙飞得起来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们也来，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是被我打过分数的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打分数…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，那边锁紧一点\N听说你们没抽中好机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过魏斯洛队长\N有我们帮忙就没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小子叫莫蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是个刚出炉的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是从克劳索拉斯号\N跳槽过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫蓝．谢兰度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个都很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有比女的先锋艇驾驶员\N更恐怖的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会认清她的真面目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比赛期间\N我会负责照顾艾儿薇丝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她一直不肯\N离开那两个孩子身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好先让你的眼晴\N适应一下黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零点准时动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，他们只会碍手碍脚而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和业余的一起飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个领航员\N在前些日子的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然还会发生红视现象\N太没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在玩家家酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的就是这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在着急什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说塔琪安娜．魏斯洛\N不过就是这种程度的驾驶员吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是自找罪受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好可怜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的是我们好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿她就要把\N气出在我们身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她长得那么可爱的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是不能靠外表来判断的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,譬如说那边那位伊萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人为什么老是在生气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要飞起来的话\N干脆重新组装比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下不彻底改装可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确\N连机身架构都受损成这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但会让机翼摇晃\N操纵杆也会变重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子比原先想像得还难处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.92,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，克劳士你们好厉害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿你也是个\N很厉害的机械师呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.93,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下可以向旋风霍克炫耀了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他我们参加了这个比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要炫耀的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了也要跟\N大肥鸡和鼻毛小子炫耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用这架\N第一次乘坐的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这第一次飞的比赛路线上\N飞完全程的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该就表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们作为驾驶员的本事\N也更上了一层楼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也向大风暴区\N更迈进了一步对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？我听不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说要好好努力比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK！克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿，我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是去把事情做个处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇她会成为一个\N顶尖的机械师的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.97,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，我现在飞在\N地平洞窟里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，新来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了，你坐在那里不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有上厕所的时候才可以离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里面装了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了魏斯洛队长好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个单纯的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能拥有像你这么好的后辈\N我实在太幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于比赛的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要设施的警备\N要比想像中来得更严密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是按照当初的计划进行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了，塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果状况有变\N我会立刻见机行事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍卖会那边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18：00，开始时间没有变更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.76,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三，二，一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次作战需要的是准确性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，英麦曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想见你，英麦曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想对我家的克劳士做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个时候\N发生红视现象的女孩是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.07,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下，我觉得您还是\N先报上自己的名字比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.61,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，我是迪奥．艾拉克莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样\N你都已经被我击落两次了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你都忘了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你是基尔特公会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？基尔特公会！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不准动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来打声招呼而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会把艾儿交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我倒是完全无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比较想和你\N在比赛里飞个高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果英麦曼你要出场的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想拿出真本事来比比看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字不叫英麦曼好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你是英麦曼\N你就是英麦曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这样如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了\N你就把你的名字告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常应该是说输了才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉，我们回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.45,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你是那个时候\N驾驶红色那架的人对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要来妨碍我们\N随便飞飞就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然要维持原定计划吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要变更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被个难搞的家伙缠上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底是来干嘛的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是敌人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好我有跟着戴芬妮一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.31,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被您姊姊听到了\N不晓得她会怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要向戴芬妮好好道谢就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那人最喜欢听人奉承了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位戴芬妮姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长她太乱来了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连引擎都还没热说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.94,0:16:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成是那个基尔特小子\N踩到她哪根神经了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是引擎的问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才明明还好好的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我争口气呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳地亚管里面的空气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经排干净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,节流管的状况呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用慌张，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心，一定可以起动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳地亚情况怎样，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次相当的安定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个瞌睡虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡虫，瞌睡虫加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝你不要给我乱跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强，首先要先习惯一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不习惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.32,0:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这种错综复杂的路线\N是不可能飞完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜\N记得我们的目的并不是获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领先的是我唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人还真好懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机身调整做得还挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不会摇晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎的声音也很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可得感谢我的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来应该是可以\N飞个八小时没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到预定地点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把速度降低\N我想测量最好的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，这是任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等第二圈再来行动也不迟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先和那家伙拉开距离才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近预定地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼还没到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去接他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜机通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一圈12分05秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长她已经完全把目的给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来玩吧，英麦曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐你旁边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.46,0:19:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在场的各位\N欢迎你们大驾光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是地平洞窟的负责人贾卡罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.07,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我们也准备了许多\N可以让各位眼晴一亮的拍卖品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还请各位慢慢欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先看第一件拍卖品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把剑莫非是雷德克里夫的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个纹章相信在座\N应该有很多人都知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.45,0:19:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是英年早逝的不世出名匠\N雷德克里夫亲手所打造的宝剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分适合作为今夜的开幕珍品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起拍价60万克劳地亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,65万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,67万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,70万克劳地亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,75万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼式回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才那个回转怎样，鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，线条取的非常漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，接下来是剪式飞行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是费尔邦的项链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎都不合你的意是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就看你\N完全不为所动的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是有什么东西要找吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.40,0:20:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看起来\N似乎也对拍卖没么兴趣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.87,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经找到\N我想要的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只需要\N把它弄到手就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近预定地点\N把速度降低，塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度降低百分之二十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢从我的头上飞过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三，二，一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点掌握失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不赖嘛，英麦曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.15,0:21:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信各位都曾经听说过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的存在相当于上帝的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到它就等于得到了整个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.12,0:21:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过至今从来没有人\N看过它真正的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们贾卡罗财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.40,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为被选中的各位安排了这个\N据说是可以进入EXILE之门的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.27,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚终极的拍卖品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.07,0:21:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别老是把我当个病人一样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起拍价五百万克劳地亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千万克劳地亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千万！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.25,0:22:39.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.02,0:22:46.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.16,0:22:57.23,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.30,0:23:02.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.91,0:23:11.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.69,0:23:17.56,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.62,0:23:23.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.43,0:23:29.23,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.30,0:23:35.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.08,0:23:47.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.59,0:23:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回预告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.36,0:23:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.56,0:23:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然不能没有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管别人怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.37,0:24:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的领航员只有你拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.93,0:24:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.64,0:24:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这次比赛结束以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就打算有件事要跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.37,0:24:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.71,0:24:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第十话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.25,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,设陷诈骗\NSwindle
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.75,0:24:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定哦，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.99,0:24:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，一言为定
